{"tid":2073023,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"俄州駁回禁集會申請 數百對立群眾聚集  無視疫情示威 特朗普照造勢","createTime":"2020-06-21T04:37:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T05:03:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"61cfac00e4c74499ca097f82f4d8dbe362609c10","tid":2073023,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:37:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200621/DHYHF6IZAIWTMI6AYENUCWJJJA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200621%2FDHYHF6IZAIWTMI6AYENUCWJJJA%2F&d=CgUtGs1XjGBKDnLe79D2Y72U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=40b230fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200621%2FDHYHF6IZAIWTMI6AYENUCWJJJA%2F&h=a906d1cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200621/DHYHF6IZAIWTMI6AYENUCWJJJA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n俄州駁回禁集會申請 數百對立群眾聚集 <br />\n無視疫情示威 特朗普照造勢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BGHNAMTRZDL5UNLS2QKTE2MAY4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBGHNAMTRZDL5UNLS2QKTE2MAY4.jpg&h=79440bf6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n塔爾薩前日舉行六月節慶祝活動，人頭湧湧。<br />\n<br />\n【播毒溫床】美國武漢肺炎疫情爆發以來，總統特朗普首場選舉造勢集會，在人群聚集增加播疫風險的憂慮與反種族歧視與反警暴怒潮高漲下，昨晚（香港時間今早）於俄克拉何馬州第二大城市塔爾薩（Tulsa）舉行。會前當地氣氛繃緊，支持與反對特朗普的數百人幾日前已在會場附近聚集，特朗普針對示威者的恐嚇意味推文，亦恐只火上加油。<br />\n<br />\n辦這場集會可說一波三折。。。。。。。不過俄州最高法院前日已駁回禁集會申請。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n入場者不強制戴口罩<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：「黑人華爾街」99年前三百黑人被殺<br />\n<br />\n特朗普團隊則表示，。。。。。，同意自行承擔因出席集會引致「任何疾病或受傷」的風險。<br />\n<br />\n集會日期亦曾惹風波，。。。。。，押後一天。<br />\n<br />\n惟緊張氣氛未見紓緩，。。。。。。惟拜納姆前日下午宣佈，獲特工處通知「再無需要宵禁」，即時撤令。<br />\n<br />\n他並表示，。。。。。。今次會完全不同！」<br />\n<br />\n近日聲望下滑的總統特朗普，。。。。。美國人認為國家發展方向正確。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n欲把抗疫辯論「非我即敵」<br />\n<br />\n特朗普選情進入關鍵時刻，。。。。。；萬一出現嚴重群眾感染，未來再辦集會就添變數。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普。。。。。這個想法！」<br />\n<br />\n美聯社/路透社"},{"pid":"e1d7fb2853a37887e6c6ceeaa18dd5f765961801","tid":2073023,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:38:49.000Z","msg":"大部分人無口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反香港人零確診都日日帶住<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fec69333a13a566c3f7792c0485ab0e0534e4172","tid":2073023,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1d7fb2853a37887e6c6ceeaa18dd5f765961801","tid":2073023,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:38:49.000Z","msg":"大部分人無口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反香港人零確診都日日帶住<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:42:15.000Z","msg":"背住面你點睇到佢哋冇戴口罩 ？<br />\n<br />\n 正面側面影到嗰幾個都全部有帶喎。"},{"pid":"121707e3de309c7b7c8b6280a6e6342495d9d8dc","tid":2073023,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fec69333a13a566c3f7792c0485ab0e0534e4172","tid":2073023,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1d7fb2853a37887e6c6ceeaa18dd5f765961801","tid":2073023,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:38:49.000Z","msg":"大部分人無口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反香港人零確診都日日帶住<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:42:15.000Z","msg":"背住面你點睇到佢哋冇戴口罩 ？<br />\n<br />\n 正面側面影到嗰幾個都全部有帶喎。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:42:56.000Z","msg":"自己睇侵FB啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56c8d74cc5c885f5b1d0ee55d06c8dc66e79ad85","tid":2073023,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"121707e3de309c7b7c8b6280a6e6342495d9d8dc","tid":2073023,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fec69333a13a566c3f7792c0485ab0e0534e4172","tid":2073023,"uid":25558